友會增多 咁對我地係好不利<br />\n我地應該:<br />\n1.反複引誘藍絲親友(如有)轉軑 依D其實最易入手 始於大家有一定信任 不厭其煩之下 點都會有效果 太藍個D搵日引佢落街俾黑狗屌/打下就得<br />\n2.歡迎藍店轉黃店 /扮黃。喂屌人地想做勝利球迷咪由佢囉 我地要既係趕絕藍色勢力同時壯大自己力量 好多撚樣都係為錢姐 知道入黃有生意做自然歸邊架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"推 毛魔玩抗爭真係專業級 共產黨依家果班都仲同佢差幾皮"},{"pid":"38c942d1739ede8fd401cfb666dc04470f2e7a95","tid":1785063,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11bb587e95c183f1727993099339dbeb497e8120","tid":1785063,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n明知扮黃店都好 我地都要扮fd  起碼少一個敵人"},{"pid":"b1598cb06e2321df4d47ba0f6f27d0480266df9a","tid":1785063,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"毛魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a84ea8bea43949d10eb290a9d29cbe36e137383","tid":1785063,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05492d011c271ffe00e4046de393217aee4a1524","tid":1785063,"uid":262093,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"e151f75b403eae0afcb6d37fd4ca7c4974e02782","tid":1785063,"uid":334806,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤東嘅文學修養<br />\n贏雜總幾廿條街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"佢本身係紅學家，啲詞仲要好精彩。<br />\n<br />\n講學養唔好搵個小學生比。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"數千古風流人物<br />\n還看 聖誕"},{"pid":"8b67b32c9d91c8b0eb463c9f05973800aa1984ef","tid":1785063,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8363981874d45ecf288f92ffae16f1b9be7360d9","tid":1785063,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"1224"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"連登無人會聽"},{"pid":"846def3976478f5b37903b6cfd6a9b4b757f62b7","tid":1785063,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T23:48:01